OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy start with showers or
OL,6,Flonger spells of rain. Then
OL,7,Fbrightening up from the west with
OL,8,Fscattered showers, but fewer showers
OL,9,Fin the south. Fresh to strong west or
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy evening and night
OL,13,Fwith outbreaks of rain spreading from
OL,14,Fthe southwest. Rain patchy across the
OL,15,Fsouth but heavy across Argyll. Strong
OL,16,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
