OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FRain, occasionally heavy,
OL,6,Fwill spread southeast across all parts
OL,7,Fin the morning. Then drier with a few
OL,8,Fshowers following on in the afternoon.
OL,9,FWindy at first.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold on
OL,12,FFriday and Saturday with scattered
OL,13,Fshowers, wintry on hills. Rain
OL,14,Fspreading east followed by showers on
OL,15,FSunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
